Background

Born and Raised in Hampstead, NH I grew up trudging through swamplands and playing club sports in the NH area. After four years studying Political Science and International Affairs at UNH, I am now embarking on a journey into the unknown, AKA the Boston Startup School. After analyzing the leadership and support for the program, I have decided to dip neck deep in the rushing river and see where it takes me. My past experiences in lobbying, international affairs and politics have provided me with a skill set that qualified me to join the new program. Looking into the future I hope to land a job in sales or business developement with one of the many amazing startup companies in the Boston Area. I am looking to connect with as many startups as possible so when I complete the program I can land a job with the startup that fits my personality and interests. If you want to learn more about my past experiences and careers, refer to my LinkedIn profile or send me an email at sheehanb7@gmail.com
